{
  "stem": "15174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next morning-- you know, we-- we-- some people decided that they were going to stay in Paris.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But my father said, no, we're going to get as far away from the Germans as possible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we were looking-- we wanted to find a train that was going farther south.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were told the next morning that there was this train going south.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, we got on the cattle car with a lot of other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the train went south.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, that part of the trip was-- the Germans weren't flying overhead, as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we just kept going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We kept going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we went as far as we could, which was practically to the Spanish border, in the Pyrenees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now of course, it wasn't only Jews that were fleeing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were a lot of people who were fleeing from the battle, from the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we got to this town called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We got off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think we had to get off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think it was the last stop before this-- before Spain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't have a Spanish passport so we couldn't go to Spain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so there were a bunch of refugees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't know how many there were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the French started, you know, distributing us among the town and various villages around there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we ended up in a village about two kilometers, or three kilometers from the town, called Savignac.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the townpeople were very nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They-- they-- there were some empty rooms or empty houses and they allowed us to stay there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I mean, you know, it was war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were refugees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't know from Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
